settings.description: Juggle Boomerangs without a stop and reach the goal!
You need to master number block swimming to beat this one. Watch out for Big Bass! Now with an E-Coin.
I realized that many support the series of difficult or almost impossible to win challenges, Mario escapes from the pipe with water then he goes inside to run because a wave of air chases him!...
Mario wakes up late because his youtube channel left him 5 years ago, you will have less than 8 seconds to run quite fast, put it to the test

Juggle Boomerangs without a stop and reach the goal!
(This is the optimized version for running as an e-reader dot code)
Hurry up and collect the clocks before time runs out!
